snippet: The plainclothes rookie Palm Beach Gardens police officer who fatally shot a stranded motorist last month was fired Wednesday, the city announced on Thursday.
abstract: Palm Beach Gardens, Fla, officials announce that Police Officer Nouman K Raja, who fatally shot Corey Jones in October, has been fired; federal and city officials are still investigating shooting.
lead_paragraph: The plainclothes rookie Palm Beach Gardens police officer who fatally shot a stranded motorist last month was fired Wednesday, the city announced on Thursday.

headline.main: Florida: Police Officer Who Killed Stranded Motorist Is Fired
headline.print_headline: Florida: Police Officer Who Killed Stranded Motorist Is Fired
